Subject: Re: PUBLIC CHALLENGE: (was RE: devfs again, (was RE: USB device a lloc ation) )
Sender: linux-kernel-owner@vger.kernel.org
Precedence: bulk
List-ID: <linux-kernel.vger.kernel.org>
